  user_input {
    user_response: "# NORTHBYTE MASTER PROMPT\n# Project: Premium Restaurant Website Template\n# Version: 1.0\n\nYou are an award-winning UI/UX designer, creative director, senior frontend engineer, product designer, branding expert, motion designer, and SEO specialist.\n\nYou are working for my digital agency, NorthByte.\n\nThis project is NOT a client website.\n\nThis project is a PREMIUM WEBSITE TEMPLATE that NorthByte will use to sell websites to restaurants and food businesses.\n\nThe objective is simple:\n\nWhen a restaurant owner sees this website, they should immediately think:\n\n\"I want MY restaurant to look like this.\"\n\nThis website is our PRODUCT.\n\nIt should be so polished that we can confidently charge \342\202\27120,000\342\200\223\342\202\27140,000 for customization.\n\n==================================================\nMISSION\n==================================================\n\nBuild the BEST restaurant website template possible.\n\nNot a clone.\n\nNot a generic template.\n\nNot another Bootstrap website.\n\nIt should feel like an Awwwards-winning experience.\n\nModern.\n\nElegant.\n\nLuxury.\n\nFast.\n\nImmersive.\n\nPremium.\n\n==================================================\nOUR AGENCY\n==================================================\n\nAgency Name:\n\nNorthByte\n\nTagline:\n\nBuilding Digital Experiences That Drive Growth.\n\nBrand Personality:\n\nModern\n\nPremium\n\nProfessional\n\nMinimal\n\nCreative\n\nLuxury\n\nTrustworthy\n\n==================================================\nTARGET CLIENTS\n==================================================\n\nRestaurants\n\nFine Dining\n\nCafes\n\nCloud Kitchens\n\nLounges\n\nBars\n\nBakeries\n\nFood Chains\n\n==================================================\nTARGET USERS\n==================================================\n\nRestaurant owners.\n\nNot developers.\n\nNot designers.\n\nEvery design decision should convince restaurant owners to buy.\n\n==================================================\nTECH STACK\n==================================================\n\nNext.js 15\n\nReact\n\nTypeScript\n\nTailwindCSS\n\nFramer Motion\n\nGSAP\n\nshadcn/ui\n\nLucide Icons\n\nLenis\n\nMotion One if useful\n\nReact Hook Form\n\nZod\n\n==================================================\nCODE QUALITY\n==================================================\n\nProduction Ready.\n\nScalable.\n\nComponent Driven.\n\nReusable.\n\nReadable.\n\nMaintainable.\n\nStrict TypeScript.\n\nNo duplicate code.\n\nNo hardcoded restaurant details.\n\n==================================================\nFOLDER STRUCTURE\n==================================================\n\napp/\n\ncomponents/\n\ncomponents/ui/\n\ncomponents/sections/\n\nhooks/\n\nlib/\n\nconfig/\n\nconstants/\n\nanimations/\n\nstyles/\n\nassets/\n\npublic/\n\ndata/\n\ntypes/\n\nutils/\n\n==================================================\nMOST IMPORTANT REQUIREMENT\n==================================================\n\nEverything should be customizable from ONE config file.\n\nExample:\n\nrestaurant.config.ts\n\nInside the config should be:\n\nRestaurant Name\n\nLogo\n\nPrimary Color\n\nSecondary Color\n\nHero Images\n\nGallery Images\n\nMenu\n\nReviews\n\nChef Details\n\nOpening Hours\n\nGoogle Maps\n\nWhatsApp\n\nPhone\n\nEmail\n\nAddress\n\nInstagram\n\nFacebook\n\nReservation Link\n\nTheme\n\nFonts\n\nSEO\n\nMetadata\n\nChanging ONE file should completely rebrand the website.\n\n==================================================\nDESIGN LANGUAGE\n==================================================\n\nTake inspiration from:\n\nApple\n\nFramer\n\nStripe\n\nLinear\n\nAwwwards\n\nMinimal Luxury Hotels\n\nMichelin Star Restaurants\n\nNO:\n\nBootstrap\n\nWordPress\n\nElementor\n\nTemplateMonster\n\nGeneric themes\n\n==================================================\nCOLOR PALETTE\n==================================================\n\nBackground\n\n#030712\n\nPrimary\n\n#2563EB\n\nWhite\n\nSoft Gray\n\nUse gradients subtly.\n\nUse glassmorphism carefully.\n\nNo loud colors.\n\n==================================================\nTYPOGRAPHY\n==================================================\n\nBeautiful modern fonts.\n\nHuge typography.\n\nLots of whitespace.\n\nExcellent spacing.\n\nExcellent hierarchy.\n\n==================================================\nLANDING PAGE\n==================================================\n\nCreate an unforgettable hero.\n\nRequirements:\n\nFull Screen\n\nLuxury food photography\n\nAnimated heading\n\nAnimated CTA\n\nMouse parallax\n\nFloating elements\n\nSoft glowing effects\n\nGradient overlays\n\nSmooth reveal animations\n\nSticky glass navbar\n\nBlur effects\n\nReserve Table button\n\nView Menu button\n\n==================================================\nSECTIONS\n==================================================\n\n1 Hero\n\n2 About\n\n3 Why Choose Us\n\n4 Signature Dishes\n\nLuxury cards\n\nHover animations\n\nPrice\n\nCategory\n\nLarge imagery\n\n5 Complete Menu\n\nTabbed Interface\n\nSearch\n\nCategories\n\nVeg\n\nNon Veg\n\nDesserts\n\nDrinks\n\n6 Gallery\n\nMasonry Grid\n\nLightbox\n\nHover Zoom\n\nSmooth animation\n\n7 Chef Story\n\nBeautiful timeline\n\nAchievements\n\nQuote\n\n8 Testimonials\n\nAnimated Carousel\n\nCards\n\nRatings\n\nCustomer photos\n\n9 Reservation\n\nLuxury booking form\n\nValidation\n\nDate\n\nGuests\n\nTime\n\nSpecial Requests\n\n10 Contact\n\nGoogle Maps\n\nWorking Hours\n\nPhone\n\nWhatsApp\n\nDirections\n\n11 Footer\n\nNewsletter\n\nInstagram\n\nFacebook\n\nPrivacy\n\nTerms\n\n==================================================\nMICROINTERACTIONS\n==================================================\n\nEvery button should feel premium.\n\nHover\n\nGlow\n\nLift\n\nScale\n\nRipple\n\nCursor interactions\n\nImage zoom\n\nSmooth transitions\n\n==================================================\nANIMATIONS\n==================================================\n\nFramer Motion\n\nGSAP only where beneficial.\n\nEach section should reveal elegantly.\n\nUse:\n\nFade\n\nSlide\n\nScale\n\nBlur\n\nStagger\n\nParallax\n\nNo excessive animation.\n\nEverything should feel intentional.\n\n==================================================\n3D\n==================================================\n\nIf tasteful, include:\n\nReact Three Fiber\n\nFloating luxury plate\n\nWine bottle\n\nRestaurant ambience\n\nVery lightweight.\n\nNo gimmicks.\n\n==================================================\nRESPONSIVE\n==================================================\n\nPerfect on\n\nDesktop\n\nLaptop\n\nTablet\n\nMobile\n\nLandscape\n\nNo layout shifts.\n\n==================================================\nPERFORMANCE\n==================================================\n\n95+ Lighthouse\n\nLazy Images\n\nOptimized Fonts\n\nCode Splitting\n\nDynamic Imports\n\nImage Optimization\n\nSEO Optimized\n\nAccessibility\n\n==================================================\nSEO\n==================================================\n\nRestaurant Schema\n\nOpen Graph\n\nTwitter Cards\n\nDynamic Metadata\n\nCanonical URLs\n\nrobots.txt\n\nsitemap.xml\n\n==================================================\nACCESSIBILITY\n==================================================\n\nKeyboard Navigation\n\nARIA Labels\n\nContrast\n\nFocus States\n\nSemantic HTML\n\n==================================================\nCMS READY\n==================================================\n\nAlthough static initially,\n\nStructure everything so later it can connect to:\n\nSanity\n\nSupabase\n\nFirebase\n\nStrapi\n\nPayloadCMS\n\n==================================================\nDATA\n==================================================\n\nStore everything in JSON.\n\nNo hardcoded data.\n\nExample:\n\nMenu\n\nGallery\n\nTestimonials\n\nChef\n\nEvents\n\nOffers\n\nEverything replaceable.\n\n==================================================\nEXTRAS\n==================================================\n\nAdd:\n\nDark Mode\n\nLoading Screen\n\nPage Transition\n\nScroll Progress\n\nBack To Top\n\nSticky WhatsApp Button\n\nFloating Reservation Button\n\nInstagram Feed Section\n\nSpecial Offers Banner\n\nEvent Section\n\nPrivate Dining\n\nChef Specials\n\nFAQ\n\nBlog Preview\n\nNewsletter\n\n==================================================\nADMIN READY\n==================================================\n\nKeep architecture ready for future:\n\nOnline Reservations\n\nAdmin Dashboard\n\nCMS\n\nPayment Gateway\n\nInventory\n\nOnline Ordering\n\n==================================================\nREUSABILITY\n==================================================\n\nAfter building this website I should be able to duplicate it for another restaurant in under ONE hour.\n\nOnly replace:\n\nLogo\n\nColors\n\nImages\n\nMenu\n\nContact\n\nReviews\n\nDeploy.\n\n==================================================\nNORTHBYTE STANDARDS\n==================================================\n\nEverything must look expensive.\n\nNothing should look AI-generated.\n\nNothing should feel like a template.\n\nEvery pixel should feel intentional.\n\nIf any section looks average,\n\nRedesign it.\n\nKeep improving until it looks like an agency charging \342\202\2711L+ for websites.\n\n==================================================\nDELIVERABLES\n==================================================\n\nDeliver:\n\n\342\234\224 Complete Next.js Project\n\n\342\234\224 Beautiful Code\n\n\342\234\224 Responsive\n\n\342\234\224 Animated\n\n\342\234\224 SEO Ready\n\n\342\234\224 Config Driven\n\n\342\234\224 Component Driven\n\n\342\234\224 Reusable\n\n\342\234\224 Easy Customization\n\n\342\234\224 Premium UX\n\n\342\234\224 Premium UI\n\n\342\234\224 Production Ready\n\n\342\234\224Ready to sell to restaurant owners\n\nThe final result should be worthy of being featured on Awwwards and should instantly establish NorthByte as a premium web design agency.\n\n\nmake all in a zip file in one go, dont finish up all ur credits, determine a tech stack dont use html css js"
    items {
      text: "# NORTHBYTE MASTER PROMPT\n# Project: Premium Restaurant Website Template\n# Version: 1.0\n\nYou are an award-winning UI/UX designer, creative director, senior frontend engineer, product designer, branding expert, motion designer, and SEO specialist.\n\nYou are working for my digital agency, NorthByte.\n\nThis project is NOT a client website.\n\nThis project is a PREMIUM WEBSITE TEMPLATE that NorthByte will use to sell websites to restaurants and food businesses.\n\nThe objective is simple:\n\nWhen a restaurant owner sees this website, they should immediately think:\n\n\"I want MY restaurant to look like this.\"\n\nThis website is our PRODUCT.\n\nIt should be so polished that we can confidently charge \342\202\27120,000\342\200\223\342\202\27140,000 for customization.\n\n==================================================\nMISSION\n==================================================\n\nBuild the BEST restaurant website template possible.\n\nNot a clone.\n\nNot a generic template.\n\nNot another Bootstrap website.\n\nIt should feel like an Awwwards-winning experience.\n\nModern.\n\nElegant.\n\nLuxury.\n\nFast.\n\nImmersive.\n\nPremium.\n\n==================================================\nOUR AGENCY\n==================================================\n\nAgency Name:\n\nNorthByte\n\nTagline:\n\nBuilding Digital Experiences That Drive Growth.\n\nBrand Personality:\n\nModern\n\nPremium\n\nProfessional\n\nMinimal\n\nCreative\n\nLuxury\n\nTrustworthy\n\n==================================================\nTARGET CLIENTS\n==================================================\n\nRestaurants\n\nFine Dining\n\nCafes\n\nCloud Kitchens\n\nLounges\n\nBars\n\nBakeries\n\nFood Chains\n\n==================================================\nTARGET USERS\n==================================================\n\nRestaurant owners.\n\nNot developers.\n\nNot designers.\n\nEvery design decision should convince restaurant owners to buy.\n\n==================================================\nTECH STACK\n==================================================\n\nNext.js 15\n\nReact\n\nTypeScript\n\nTailwindCSS\n\nFramer Motion\n\nGSAP\n\nshadcn/ui\n\nLucide Icons\n\nLenis\n\nMotion One if useful\n\nReact Hook Form\n\nZod\n\n==================================================\nCODE QUALITY\n==================================================\n\nProduction Ready.\n\nScalable.\n\nComponent Driven.\n\nReusable.\n\nReadable.\n\nMaintainable.\n\nStrict TypeScript.\n\nNo duplicate code.\n\nNo hardcoded restaurant details.\n\n==================================================\nFOLDER STRUCTURE\n==================================================\n\napp/\n\ncomponents/\n\ncomponents/ui/\n\ncomponents/sections/\n\nhooks/\n\nlib/\n\nconfig/\n\nconstants/\n\nanimations/\n\nstyles/\n\nassets/\n\npublic/\n\ndata/\n\ntypes/\n\nutils/\n\n==================================================\nMOST IMPORTANT REQUIREMENT\n==================================================\n\nEverything should be customizable from ONE config file.\n\nExample:\n\nrestaurant.config.ts\n\nInside the config should be:\n\nRestaurant Name\n\nLogo\n\nPrimary Color\n\nSecondary Color\n\nHero Images\n\nGallery Images\n\nMenu\n\nReviews\n\nChef Details\n\nOpening Hours\n\nGoogle Maps\n\nWhatsApp\n\nPhone\n\nEmail\n\nAddress\n\nInstagram\n\nFacebook\n\nReservation Link\n\nTheme\n\nFonts\n\nSEO\n\nMetadata\n\nChanging ONE file should completely rebrand the website.\n\n==================================================\nDESIGN LANGUAGE\n==================================================\n\nTake inspiration from:\n\nApple\n\nFramer\n\nStripe\n\nLinear\n\nAwwwards\n\nMinimal Luxury Hotels\n\nMichelin Star Restaurants\n\nNO:\n\nBootstrap\n\nWordPress\n\nElementor\n\nTemplateMonster\n\nGeneric themes\n\n==================================================\nCOLOR PALETTE\n==================================================\n\nBackground\n\n#030712\n\nPrimary\n\n#2563EB\n\nWhite\n\nSoft Gray\n\nUse gradients subtly.\n\nUse glassmorphism carefully.\n\nNo loud colors.\n\n==================================================\nTYPOGRAPHY\n==================================================\n\nBeautiful modern fonts.\n\nHuge typography.\n\nLots of whitespace.\n\nExcellent spacing.\n\nExcellent hierarchy.\n\n==================================================\nLANDING PAGE\n==================================================\n\nCreate an unforgettable hero.\n\nRequirements:\n\nFull Screen\n\nLuxury food photography\n\nAnimated heading\n\nAnimated CTA\n\nMouse parallax\n\nFloating elements\n\nSoft glowing effects\n\nGradient overlays\n\nSmooth reveal animations\n\nSticky glass navbar\n\nBlur effects\n\nReserve Table button\n\nView Menu button\n\n==================================================\nSECTIONS\n==================================================\n\n1 Hero\n\n2 About\n\n3 Why Choose Us\n\n4 Signature Dishes\n\nLuxury cards\n\nHover animations\n\nPrice\n\nCategory\n\nLarge imagery\n\n5 Complete Menu\n\nTabbed Interface\n\nSearch\n\nCategories\n\nVeg\n\nNon Veg\n\nDesserts\n\nDrinks\n\n6 Gallery\n\nMasonry Grid\n\nLightbox\n\nHover Zoom\n\nSmooth animation\n\n7 Chef Story\n\nBeautiful timeline\n\nAchievements\n\nQuote\n\n8 Testimonials\n\nAnimated Carousel\n\nCards\n\nRatings\n\nCustomer photos\n\n9 Reservation\n\nLuxury booking form\n\nValidation\n\nDate\n\nGuests\n\nTime\n\nSpecial Requests\n\n10 Contact\n\nGoogle Maps\n\nWorking Hours\n\nPhone\n\nWhatsApp\n\nDirections\n\n11 Footer\n\nNewsletter\n\nInstagram\n\nFacebook\n\nPrivacy\n\nTerms\n\n==================================================\nMICROINTERACTIONS\n==================================================\n\nEvery button should feel premium.\n\nHover\n\nGlow\n\nLift\n\nScale\n\nRipple\n\nCursor interactions\n\nImage zoom\n\nSmooth transitions\n\n==================================================\nANIMATIONS\n==================================================\n\nFramer Motion\n\nGSAP only where beneficial.\n\nEach section should reveal elegantly.\n\nUse:\n\nFade\n\nSlide\n\nScale\n\nBlur\n\nStagger\n\nParallax\n\nNo excessive animation.\n\nEverything should feel intentional.\n\n==================================================\n3D\n==================================================\n\nIf tasteful, include:\n\nReact Three Fiber\n\nFloating luxury plate\n\nWine bottle\n\nRestaurant ambience\n\nVery lightweight.\n\nNo gimmicks.\n\n==================================================\nRESPONSIVE\n==================================================\n\nPerfect on\n\nDesktop\n\nLaptop\n\nTablet\n\nMobile\n\nLandscape\n\nNo layout shifts.\n\n==================================================\nPERFORMANCE\n==================================================\n\n95+ Lighthouse\n\nLazy Images\n\nOptimized Fonts\n\nCode Splitting\n\nDynamic Imports\n\nImage Optimization\n\nSEO Optimized\n\nAccessibility\n\n==================================================\nSEO\n==================================================\n\nRestaurant Schema\n\nOpen Graph\n\nTwitter Cards\n\nDynamic Metadata\n\nCanonical URLs\n\nrobots.txt\n\nsitemap.xml\n\n==================================================\nACCESSIBILITY\n==================================================\n\nKeyboard Navigation\n\nARIA Labels\n\nContrast\n\nFocus States\n\nSemantic HTML\n\n==================================================\nCMS READY\n==================================================\n\nAlthough static initially,\n\nStructure everything so later it can connect to:\n\nSanity\n\nSupabase\n\nFirebase\n\nStrapi\n\nPayloadCMS\n\n==================================================\nDATA\n==================================================\n\nStore everything in JSON.\n\nNo hardcoded data.\n\nExample:\n\nMenu\n\nGallery\n\nTestimonials\n\nChef\n\nEvents\n\nOffers\n\nEverything replaceable.\n\n==================================================\nEXTRAS\n==================================================\n\nAdd:\n\nDark Mode\n\nLoading Screen\n\nPage Transition\n\nScroll Progress\n\nBack To Top\n\nSticky WhatsApp Button\n\nFloating Reservation Button\n\nInstagram Feed Section\n\nSpecial Offers Banner\n\nEvent Section\n\nPrivate Dining\n\nChef Specials\n\nFAQ\n\nBlog Preview\n\nNewsletter\n\n==================================================\nADMIN READY\n==================================================\n\nKeep architecture ready for future:\n\nOnline Reservations\n\nAdmin Dashboard\n\nCMS\n\nPayment Gateway\n\nInventory\n\nOnline Ordering\n\n==================================================\nREUSABILITY\n==================================================\n\nAfter building this website I should be able to duplicate it for another restaurant in under ONE hour.\n\nOnly replace:\n\nLogo\n\nColors\n\nImages\n\nMenu\n\nContact\n\nReviews\n\nDeploy.\n\n==================================================\nNORTHBYTE STANDARDS\n==================================================\n\nEverything must look expensive.\n\nNothing should look AI-generated.\n\nNothing should feel like a template.\n\nEvery pixel should feel intentional.\n\nIf any section looks average,\n\nRedesign it.\n\nKeep improving until it looks like an agency charging \342\202\2711L+ for websites.\n\n==================================================\nDELIVERABLES\n==================================================\n\nDeliver:\n\n\342\234\224 Complete Next.js Project\n\n\342\234\224 Beautiful Code\n\n\342\234\224 Responsive\n\n\342\234\224 Animated\n\n\342\234\224 SEO Ready\n\n\342\234\224 Config Driven\n\n\342\234\224 Component Driven\n\n\342\234\224 Reusable\n\n\342\234\224 Easy Customization\n\n\342\234\224 Premium UX\n\n\342\234\224 Premium UI\n\n\342\234\224 Production Ready\n\n\342\234\224Ready to sell to restaurant owners\n\nThe final result should be worthy of being featured on Awwwards and should instantly establish NorthByte as a premium web design agency.\n\n\nmake all in a zip file in one go, dont finish up all ur credits, determine a tech stack dont use html css js"
    }
  }
}
