        lines {
          text: "    bio: \"Kenji spent 15 years as apprentice and sous chef at the legendary Sukiyabashi Jiro block. He relocated to set up Sakura, importing premium binchotan coals and hand-crafted shoyu to introduce the uncompromised Tokyo Ginza discipline.\","
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
