        }
        lines {
          text: "    bio: \"Raised in the hills of San Gimignano, Chef Giovanni inherited his grandmother\'s pasta cutter and her strict iron will. He brings high-spirited laughter, heavy rustic pans, and uncompromising olive oil selections.\","
